content.description:
This proposal is to vote for an upgrade to v1.3.0, which will be branched off and released from master branch commit c4902de745fae67a40aaf3047ad1304334975121.
Once the proposal passes the upgrade will take effect at height 1423600 or approximately on Feb 1st 4PM EST (9PM UTC).

link: https://github.com/certikfoundation/shentu/commit/c4902de745fae67a40aaf3047ad1304334975121

Upgrade instructions:
	1. Download or build the latest binaries
	2. Halt certikd process before the upgrade height(=1423600).
	3. Replace the binaries with the latest v1.3.0 binaries
	4. start certikd process with the new certikd binary.

NOTE: You do NOT have to run 'certikd unsafe-reset-all' for this upgrade. Running 'certikd unsafe-reset-all' will reset the chain's data, and you will have to re-sync from height 0.

The version includes a bugfix for shield service fee distribution with some minor API improvements and tests.
content.title: v1.3.0 Upgrade Proposal

content.description:
This proposal will update the expired client on channel-8 between the Osmosis-1 and Shentu-2.2. Client 07-tendermint-9 has been expired due to the recent Osmosis chain halt of the past few days.

- By voting **YES**, the Shentu stakers, voice their support to unfreeze IBC channel-8 between shentu-2.2 and osmosis-1.

- By voting NO, the Shentu stakers voice their dissent to unfreeze IBC channel-8 between shentu-2.2 and osmosis-1.

**Details:**

In the case that this proposal goes through, client 07-tendermint-9 state will be substituted by the state of client 07-tendermint-23, what will unfreeze channel-8 and will allow users to transfer tokens between Osmosis and Shentu again.
content.title: Update Osmosis Client on Shentu

content.description:
This proposal is to employ Jinchao as a Shentu Growth Manager. Jinchao's 5+ years in digital marketing, performance marketing, and PR equip her to elevate Shentu's digital presence and community engagement. Her role will focus on:

 - Enhancing Visibility : Enhancing Shentu's digital presence and performance marketing.
 - Communication strategies : Building effective communication strategies to grow the Shentu community. Jinchao will be a part-time resource, dedicating an average of 20-30 hours a week on average performing in herShentu Growth Manager role. with compensation in Shentu from the "Shentu Community" Validator node. The Yes vote will be used as a signature of the Shentu Validators/Stakeholders and this will serve as a Contract between the Shentu Chain and Jinchao.
